snippet.title: Nintendo Switch 「QV」 Meet the Characters #2: Varon
snippet.description:
Proudly presenting QV, an inter-dimensional action adventure game for Nintendo Switch!
This time, we meet Varon!
A penguin from another world, Varon explores the ruins with Quby.
How will Varon cooperate with Quby in the ruins?

- Official Twitter Account : https://twitter.com/QV_NEWS
